      "id": "PopularPost321499",
      "post_content": "This would be better, but too good, at just one mana. As is, I don't think it's Artifact Destruction mode is good enough most of the time.   \n  \nSpecifically in Modern Masters Draft, it's very useful- probably one of the better Artifact Destroyers. But Modern Masters chose this instead of [Shattering Spree](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shattering Spree) because it wanted Artifacts relatively playable.",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost321499\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">This would be better, but too good, at just one mana. As is, I don't think it's Artifact Destruction mode is good enough most of the time. <br/><br/>Specifically in Modern Masters Draft, it's very useful- probably one of the better Artifact Destroyers. But Modern Masters chose this instead of <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shattering Spree\">Shattering Spree</a> because it wanted Artifacts relatively playable.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46041\">DarthParallax</span>\r\n                                (6/11/2013 3:38:52 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.pn